@jreback Two other things: 
- `astype('timedelta64[h]')` does not work on TimedeltaIndex as it does on a timedelta series (to do conversions as is explained in the docs). Should that?
- the `round` method of Timestamp would maybe also be interesting for TimedeltaIndex (and TimedeltaProperties)? -> although this is maybe a broader issue: support for datetime/timedelta in Series.round
